# Each entry below exceeds the ceiling stated in Invariant #3 of
# docs/plans/2026-04-24-top-tier-roadmap.md:
#   - src/core (and current core/):    500 lines
#   - src/modules (and current modules/): 800 lines
#   - Root-level entry points:         500 lines
#
# Every file here is scheduled for refactor in a named roadmap phase. New files
# MUST respect the ceiling at creation time — .size-ignore is not a place to
# add new entries; it only grandfathers what already exists on 2026-04-24.
#
# Maintenance rule: when a phase completes, its files here should have dropped
# below the ceiling and be removed from this file. If a file remains after its
# target phase is "done," the refactor is incomplete.
#
# Format: <path>  # <lines> lines — <target phase / rationale>

